\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104luz1665702709079.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/luz1665702709079.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/luz1665702709079.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"luz1665702709079\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Global Variable\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Global Variable is a Development Object that defines a typed variable that can be accessed by all ProcScript in the application.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"luz1665702709079__section_w232ab1b5b1_w233ab1b5_w234ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"luz1665702709079__section_w235ab1b5b3_w236ab1b5_w237ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d495884e56\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">var</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijz1665702550775.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijz1665702550775.html\" title=\"An Untyped Library is a Main Development Object that defines a collection of objects that may be of different types, and which can be reused or accessed by other objects during development or at runtime.\">Untyped Library</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">$$register@<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>.prc</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luz1665702709079__table_d10646e1_d10647e1_d10648e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lib:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>:var:<var class=\"keyword varname\">VariableName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"luz1665702709079__section_w238ab1b5b5_w239ab1b5_w240ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d495884e255\">\n                     \n Properties\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luz1665702709079__li_d38834e1_d38835e1_d38836e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luz1665702709079__li_d38837e1_d38838e1_d38839e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luz1665702709079__li_d38840e1_d38841e1_d38842e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aww1665702586248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aww1665702586248.html\" title=\"Uniface data type to use for this field, variable, or parameter. The default value is S (String).\">Data Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luz1665702709079__li_d38843e1_d38844e1_d38845e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aym1665702709149.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aym1665702709149.html\" title=\"Interface definition for a variable or operation parameter with Data Type Handle or XMLStream.\">Classification</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luz1665702709079__li_d38846e1_d38847e1_d38848e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"egj1665702709221.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/egj1665702709221.html\" title=\"Specify a display format for the global variable, which can be used to format the data for display or string substitution.\">Display Format (Global Variable)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luz1665702709079__li_d38849e1_d38850e1_d38851e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bck1665702654827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bck1665702654827.html\" title=\"Extended description of the global object.\">Comments</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"luz1665702709079__section_w241ab1b5b7_w242ab1b5_w243ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d495884e337\">\n                     \n Specialization\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"luz1665702709079__p_d96020e1_d96021e1_d96022e1\">Global Variable specializes Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luz1665702709079__li_d38852e1_d38853e1_d38854e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"luz1665702709079__p_d96023e1_d96024e1_d96025e1\">It has a library as parent object.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luz1665702709079__li_d38855e1_d38856e1_d38857e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"luz1665702709079__p_d96026e1_d96027e1_d96028e1\">It has no child objects.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/clk1665702551274.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Variables</a><p>Variables are placeholders for data whose value can change during the runtime duration of the ProcScript module, component, or application for which they have scope. The scope is determined by where they are declared.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/por1705566942408.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Working with Global Variables</a><p>Global variables are accessible to all ProcScript in an application's components, and to global ProcScripts that use the same library or the system library.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614459\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614459\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Global Variable Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Global Variable A Global Variable is a Development Object that defines a typed variable that can be accessed by all ProcScript in the application. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: var Main Development Object? No Part of: Untyped Library Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: $$register@ LibraryName .prc URI format: lib: LibraryName :var: VariableName Properties Name Description Data Type Classification Display Format (Global Variable) Comments Specialization Global Variable specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a library as parent object. It has no child objects. Related Links Variables Variables are placeholders for data whose value can change during the runtime duration of the ProcScript module, component, or application for which they have scope. The scope is determined by where they are declared. Working with Global Variables Global variables are accessible to all ProcScript in an application's components, and to global ProcScripts that use the same library or the system library. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}